OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FPublic bodies must face scrutiny over
OL,8,Fthe death of murdered baby Preston
OL,9,FDavey, a hearing has heard.
OL,11,FThe senior coroner for Blackpool and
OL,12,FFylde said it is "highly likely" he
OL,13,Fwill hold an inquest into the death of
OL,14,Fthe 13-month-old.
OL,16,FPreston was murdered by his 37-year-
OL,17,Fold adoptive parent Jamie Farley
OL,18,Fduring a sex attack on 27 July 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe had adopted the child with his
OL,8,Fpartner John McGowan-Fazakerley, 32,
OL,9,Ffour months before the youngster's
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FBut they had treated the child as
OL,13,Ftheir "plaything", with the baby
OL,14,Fsuffering "unremitting abuse" of sex
OL,15,Fassaults and physical attacks at their
OL,16,FBlackpool home.
OL,26,@uD@GOUuD@QO]vD@KOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FVarley, described as "evil" and a
OL,8,F"sadist" by detectives, was given a
OL,9,Fwhole life term for murder and 24
OL,10,Fother offences after an eight-week
OL,11,Ftrial ending in June.
OL,13,FHis co-defendant was jailed for 25
OL,14,Fyears.
OL,16,FPreston had been taken to Blackpool
OL,17,FVictoria Hospital three times before
OL,18,Fhis death and seen by a "battery of
OL,19,Fprofessionals" including medical
OL,20,Fstaff, social workers and welfare
OL,21,Fofficers from various bodies.
OL,26,@oD@VOUoD@[O]pD@AOUpD@HO]zD@YOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FSenior Coroner Alan Wilson told
OL,8,FBlackpool Coroner's Court an inquest
OL,9,Fhad initially been opened shortly
OL,10,Fafter Preston's death but was then
OL,11,Fsuspended while police investigated,
OL,12,Fculminating in the trial and
OL,13,Fconviction of his adoptive parents.
OL,15,FMr Wilson said he had to consider
OL,16,Fwhether an inquest should continue,
OL,17,Fgiven "relevant issues" had already
OL,18,Fbeen heard during the eight-week
OL,19,Fcriminal trial.
OL,26,@yD@GOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHowever, while he said he would not
OL,8,Fmake a final decision today, it was
OL,9,F"highly likely" one would take place
OL,10,Fin autumn 2027.
OL,12,FMr Wilson said: "I feel there's
OL,13,Fsufficient reason to resume. There are
OL,14,Facts and omissions of public
OL,15,Fauthorities that need to be
OL,16,Fscrutinised in a public hearing in
OL,17,Fwhich Preston's family can participate.
OL,19,F"It's clearly going to be a wide-
OL,20,Franging inquiry."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@OO]tD@QOU{D@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe coroner said he was aware there
OL,8,Fhad been calls for a public inquiry,
OL,9,Fbut his role meant that was not a
OL,10,Fmatter for himself to consider, but to
OL,11,Fproceed on the basis of whether or not
OL,12,Fto hold an inquest.
OL,14,FThe court heard Oldham Safeguarding
OL,15,FChildren's Partnership, had resumed a
OL,16,Freview into Preston's death, following
OL,17,Fits suspension for the criminal trial
OL,18,Fto take place.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThis review is likely only to be
OL,8,Fcompleted by January 2027, and the
OL,9,Finquest cannot be held before then,
OL,10,Fthe court heard.
OL,12,FPreston was born while his mother was
OL,13,Fin custody and a place in a mother and
OL,14,Fbaby unit in prison was refused, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard.
OL,17,FInstead, he was taken from her by a
OL,18,Fcourt order from Oldham Council and
OL,19,Fplaced with temporary adoptive parents
OL,20,Fbefore being adopted by Varley and
OL,21,FMcGowan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FAdoption Now, which handled Preston's
OL,8,Fadoption, was represented at the
OL,9,Fhearing, along with Bolton Council,
OL,10,Fdescribed as the "host" council for
OL,11,Fthe body.
OL,13,FWhile Oldham Council managed Preston's
OL,14,Fadoption, Bolton Council also a had a
OL,15,Frole, the hearing was told.
OL,17,FAlso present were lawyers for Gary
OL,18,FNolan, Preston's father, along with
OL,19,Flegal representatives for the NHS
OL,20,Ftrust running Blackpool Victoria
OL,21,FHospital.
OL,26,@rD@ROUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FWhether South Shore Academy, the high
OL,8,Fschool where Varley worked should be
OL,9,Finvolved in the inquest, is a matter
OL,10,Fstill to be resolved, the hearing was
OL,11,Ftold.
OL,13,FAnd also to be decided is whether
OL,14,FLancashire Police should have lawyers
OL,15,Frepresenting the force at an inquest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784636313
OL,3,C'Scrutiny' needed over death of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler Preston Davey, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe trial heard their officers had
OL,8,Fbeen called after Preston had been
OL,9,Ftaken for the first time to hospital
OL,10,Fsuffering injuries and safeguarding
OL,11,Fconcerns were raised, but no further
OL,12,Faction was taken.
OL,14,FMr Wilson adjourned for a further
OL,15,Fhearing to be held in October, telling
OL,16,FPreston's father: "Please accept
OL,17,Feveryone's condolences, I'm conscious
OL,18,Fwe are approaching his anniversary."
OL,26,@xD@SOUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
